# Smart Library Request Workflow in ServiceNow

## Task 4 – Execution Roadmap

### Project Overview

The Smart Library Request Workflow is a ServiceNow-based application developed to automate library operations such as book management, borrow request processing, workflow approvals, role-based access control, and reporting.

This roadmap outlines the complete implementation plan for developing, testing, and deploying the application.

